title: Sepsis gram-positive TP1
extract_protocol: Total RNA extraction using guanidinium thiocyanate (Ambion) according to manufacturer's protocol.
label: biotin
label_protocol: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix one-cycle labelling protocol from 1ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual 2001, Affymetrix)
hybridization_protocol: Following fragmentation, 15ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on GeneChip U133 plus 2.0 arrays.  GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using an Affymetrix GCS3000 7G 4C scanner with autoloader
data_processing: Affymetrix CEL files were imported into the RMA software (Bioconductor) to compute probeset summaries.  Quantile nomalization was used.
